short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A chrome extension that changes the default colours of the GAE admin console and the google cloud console based on app ID.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Alters css of the Google app engine admin console based on app id in order to provide a simple visual cue as to which environment is currently in use.

1.0.0 - Correction to version number scheme.  First full release.

0.0.2 - Additional support for the new cloud console.

0.0.1 - Supports app id's containing '-dev', '-test', and '-demo' to denote environment.  All other app id's will result in an unaltered styling.
